<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1018,1439]" pageId="9" pageNumber="514">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,613,1054,1079]" pageId="9" pageNumber="514">
Condition of the 
<typeStatus box="[409,473,1054,1079]" pageId="9" pageNumber="514">types</typeStatus>
. 
<typeStatus box="[488,608,1054,1079]" pageId="9" pageNumber="514">Lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Wings slightly rubbed, otherwise in perfect condition. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1253,1436,1054,1079]" pageId="9" pageNumber="514">
<typeStatus box="[1253,1431,1054,1079]" pageId="9" pageNumber="514">Paralectotypes</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Most 
<typeStatus box="[216,378,1090,1115]" pageId="9" pageNumber="514">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
are in very good condition, but a few have the forewings worn, while one of the females has lost its abdomen.
